Kubernetes,is,an,open,source,standard,for,developing,apps,that,make,containerized,applications,deployable,scalable,and,easy,to,manage,in,different,host,clusters,The,Kubernetes,API,provides,container,centric,infrastructure,for,implementing,fast,seamless,and,predictable,application,development,operations,The,API,sends,requests,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format